    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0783a27"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>袁州仰山<persName key="A009491">慧寂</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0783a28"/><persName key="A009491">釋慧寂</persName>，俗姓葉，<placeName key="PL000000030712">韶州<anchor xml:id="beg0783001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>須</sic><corr>湞</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0783001"/>昌</placeName>人也。登<date key="j20209252021289" from-iso="+0821-01-01" to-iso="+0821-12-31">年十五</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0783a29"/>懇請出家，父母都不聽允止。<date key="j20216552022019" from-iso="+0823-01-01" to-iso="+0823-12-31">十七</date>再求堂<pb ed="T" n="0783b" xml:id="T50.2061.0783b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0783b01"/>親，猶豫未決。其夜有<anchor xml:id="beg0783002"/>白<anchor xml:id="end0783002"/>光二道從<placeName key="PL000000030578">曹溪</placeName>發<lb
ed="T" n="0783b02"/>來，直貫其舍。<anchor xml:id="beg0783003"/>時父<anchor xml:id="end0783003"/>母乃悟<persName key="A009491">是子</persName>至誠之所<lb
ed="T" n="0783b03"/>感也。<persName key="A009491">寂</persName>乃斷左無名指及小指，器藉跪致<lb
ed="T" n="0783b04"/>堂階曰：「答謝劬勞如此！」父<anchor xml:id="beg0783004"/>母<add resp="sgsz">知</add><anchor xml:id="end0783004"/>其不可留，<lb
ed="T" n="0783b05"/>捨之。依<placeName key="PL000000030578">南華寺</placeName><persName key="A010621">通禪師</persName><ptr target="#n563"/>下削染，年及<date key="j20220202022385" from-iso="+0824-01-01" to-iso="+0824-12-31">十八</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0783b06"/>尚為息慈。營持道具，行尋知識。先見<persName key="A008874">耽源</persName>。<lb
ed="T" n="0783b07"/>數年，良有所得。後參<persName key="A001984">大溈山禪師</persName>，提誘哀<lb
ed="T" n="0783b08"/>之。棲泊十四五載，而足跋，時號<persName key="A009491"><anchor xml:id="beg0783005"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>跛</sic><corr>跋</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0783005"/>脚驅烏</persName>。<lb
ed="T" n="0783b09"/>凡於商攉，多示其相。時<persName key="A010622">韋胄</persName>就<persName key="A009491">寂</persName>請伽<lb
ed="T" n="0783b10"/><anchor xml:id="beg0783006"/>陀<anchor xml:id="end0783006"/>，乃將紙畫規圓相，圓圍下注云：「思而知<lb
ed="T" n="0783b11"/>之，落第二頭。云不思而知，落第三首。」乃封<lb
ed="T" n="0783b12"/>呈達。自爾有若干勢以示學人，謂之<placeName key="PL000000019591">仰山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0783b13"/>門風也。海眾摳衣得道者，不可勝計，往往<lb
ed="T" n="0783b14"/>有神異之者，<anchor xml:id="beg0783sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>條</sic><corr>倐</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0783sgsz3"/>來忽去，人皆不測。後勅追<lb
ed="T" n="0783b15"/>諡大師，曰<persName key="A009491">智通</persName>，塔號妙光矣。今傳《仰山法<lb
ed="T" n="0783b16"/>示成圖相》，行于代也。</p>
